title: FOUNDERS' DAY Photos & Results
body_text:
Founder Megill vs. First Lady Nittoso in a classic husband-wife showdown, unlimited gold ball team regeneration, the patriotic "Wheel of Fortune" Rimshot Contest, and the long-awaited returns of many ECD supporters including Sascha Basista, Kerrin Marchese, the Yochum family ...
EXCLUSIVE BACKSTORY!
I sent Kevin and Leah a text on January 15 that stated they could either team up against a to-be-determined duo or face-off one-on-one in ECD's first husband vs. wife match. Wouldn't you know it, KMJ responded within seconds choosing the latter. Leah surely agreed one minute later.
This was KMJ's 14th match and unprecedented 10th time in a Major ECD event. On the other hand, Leah became the first debutant captain since Kylie Casteling & Kevin O'Connell way back in 2011!
